***Colspan***
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>colspan</title>
<style>
table, th, td {
  border: 1px solid black;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  background-color:lightblue;
  padding:5px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<br>
<table style="width:100%">
  <tr>
    <th COLSPAN="2">Full Name</th>
    <th>Age</th>
  </tr>
