ID & Classes
•	Ids are unique so we can’t apply the same id to different elements as we did in classes
•	we can style only one element at a time. It is very important to note that Html documents can’t have two elements with the same ids.
•	Classes can applied to multiple elements
•	Id’s can be apply for single element

•	<!DOCTYPE html>
•	<html lang="en">
•	<head>
•	    <meta charset="UTF-8">
